episodes.title: The Cult That Killed 900 People
episodes.description:
Brief documentary on the Jonestown cult and how it lead to the deaths of over 900 people. The tale of Jonestown is one of the most chilling chapters in modern history, where belief, manipulation, and power converged into one catastrophic moment.

Subscribe: @10-MinuteHorror 

This video is for educational, artistic, and documentary purposes.
